Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
4 Lodge Drive consists of a large standalone warehouse, that can be divided into 2, 3 or 4 areas from 5,000sqm*. The Warehouse provides high truss good quality warehouse accommodation with a truss height between 12m*-14m*, is fully sprinklered and benefits from multiple roller and sliding doors.
Additional features include automatic access gates, dual road accessibility and perimeter security fencing. The site provides excellent truck circulation with full drive around capability along with extensive container storage areas also available.
Warehouse areas are available from 5,000sqm* up to the whole building 24,000sqm*
